description: Necky Looksha Sport LV (low volume) sea kayak - (almost) ONE OF A KIND!!! 14' long, 22" wide. ONLY 30 lbs. Clear Coat over "natural" Carbon Kevlar Fabric hull and deck. This boat has been dubbed the "Stealth Kayak" as the color blends into the water color and the clean deck is free from lines and such. Sized for a medium adult. If you want/need/deserve a unique boat, here you go.  Great all around sea kayak and you can paddle anywhere with confidence: river, lake, ocean, inlet, surf, etc. A day trip boat that you'll be glad to have in your quiver. The incredible light weight means that it is easy to heft up on top of the SUV plus it is fast & maneuverable. I bought it new from Schuylkill Outfitters at North Wildwood, NJ (now out of business) about about 8 years ago.  He had it listed at $3,200 because of the Carbon Kevlar construction and light weight. He told me that this was one of only 15 boats of this model made of Kevlar and it was built by kayaking fanatics in Seattle, Washington who work at the Boeing plant making carbon kevlar parts for the Black Hawk helicopter for the military.  They liked the design so much that they obtained the mold from Necky and produced 15 of these ultra light weight boats. I bought it to paddle out the inlets and surf offshore waves near Cape May & Stone Harbor, North Wildwood at  Hereford, Corson and Townsend Inlets. In very good shape; it has been used a bit but has hardly any scuffs or scratches on the bottom. Adjustable foot braces. All the fittings are there if you wanted to add a rudder kit (sorry no drop skeg)....but if you have some skills, you won't need either as it is so maneuverable. Treat yourself, you deserve it.  You'll never see another one like this on the East Coast; it is a head turner. See the reviews for the design (plastic version): http://www.paddling.net/Reviews/showReviews.html?prod=222 Please reply to posting and include your phone number. I will call you back to discuss your questions (evenings are best usually). CASH ONLY please.
title: Necky Looksha Sport LV 14' KEVLAR Sea Kayak  30 Lbs!
